### ============================================================
###   GabbyTech Academy API — REST Client Test File
###   Use with the REST Client extension in VS Code
###   Server: http://localhost:8000
### ============================================================


### ── DASHBOARD ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get school summary dashboard
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard


###


### ── STUDENTS: GET ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all students
GET http://localhost:8000/students

###

### Get all students in a specific grade (JSS1 JSS2 JSS3 SS1 SS2 SS3)
GET http://localhost:8000/students/grade/SS2

###

### Get a single student by MongoDB ID  ← replace after you POST one
GET http://localhost:8000/students/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID


###


