### ── COURSES: POST ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Create course 1
POST http://localhost:8000/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseCode": "MTH301",
  "courseName": "Further Mathematics",
  "courseShortName": "FURTHMATHS",
  "department": "Sciences",
  "subjectCategory": "WAEC",
  "gradeLevel": "SS3",
  "term": "Full Year",
  "teacherName": "Mr. Adewale Ogundimu",
  "teacherEmail": "a.ogundimu@gabbytech.edu.ng",
  "hoursPerWeek": 5,
  "maxEnrollment": 40,
  "creditUnits": 4,
  "passMark": 40,
  "isWAECSubject": true,
  "isActive": true,
  "description": "Advanced mathematics for SS3 science students preparing for WAEC. Covers calculus, vectors, and statistics.",
  "syllabusSummary": "Term 1: Calculus. Term 2: Vectors. Term 3: Statistics.",
